snippet.title: Cube de Grace | New Gameplay | Collectible Game | Indie
snippet.description:
Fortune Handlers has undergone a transformation, including a new name, story line, and setting. The game is now known as Cube de Grace.

We have created a new Steam page for Cube de Grace, which can be found at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2341200/Cube_de_Grace/. It would be incredibly helpful if you could add the game to your wish list and share the news with your friends.

We believe that this change will lay a robust foundation for the project and enable us to progress more quickly in the future.

Discord: https://discord.gg/g7fErbzuNj 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CDGgame
